Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:06.500
Birinchi savolga javob XML element 
nomi shu yerda, ya’ni TextView .

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:08.180
U ochiq burchakli qavsdan keyin keladi.

00:00:10.120 --> 00:00:13.195
Keyingisi, barcha atributlar quyidagi 
 XML elementining nomi bo‘lib, 

00:00:13.195 --> 00:00:15.750
Mana bu yerda atribut nomlarining 
tagiga chizib chiqqanman.

00:00:15.750 --> 00:00:17.960
Ular tenglik belgisining 
chap tarafida.

00:00:17.960 --> 00:00:21.180
Ular android:matn, android:matnRangi va 
boshqalarni o‘z ichiga oladi.

00:00:22.330 --> 00:00:25.440
Agar siz atributga Happy Birthday yoki rang uchun 
oq yoki qora deb qiymat bermoqchi bo‘lsangiz, 

00:00:25.440 --> 00:00:28.870
bu noto‘g‘ri, chunki ular 
atribut qiymatlari,

00:00:28.870 --> 00:00:31.450
bu yerda esa nom uchun so‘ralayapti. 

00:00:31.450 --> 00:00:34.540
Oxirgi savolda qaysi qatorda 
teg yopilganligi so‘ralgandi.

00:00:34.540 --> 00:00:36.020
U holda biz yotiq chiziqli va 

00:00:36.020 --> 00:00:39.960
yopiq burchakli qavsni oxirgi 
6-qatorda ko‘ryapmiz.

00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:42.150
Bu anglatadiki, teg o‘zi 
yopiladigan teg, 

00:00:42.150 --> 00:00:44.920
chunki biz matn view tegini mana bu yerda 
ochib keyin shu zahotiyoq uni yopib qo‘yayapmiz.

